BPCI Advanced is slated to start Oct. 1, but the AHA proposed adding two additional start date options in 2019 — Jan. 1 and April 1. "These additional start dates would expand the opportunities for applicants to be part of the initial BPCI Advanced cohorts
The BPCI Advanced model from CMS goes into effect in October, replacing the current #bundledpayments initiative. Here’s some perspective on the major provisions providers must begin considering. https://t.co/y5PeGXKIo5
